i Đất)Trích dẫn:--\"Zor-El is a Kryptonian that appears in comic books published by DC Comics. He is the younger brother of Jor-El, husband of Alura, father of Supergirl, and paternal uncle of Superman. Zor-El first appeared in Action Comics #252 (May 1959).\"Nguồn trích dẫn: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zor-El</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"62688","season":1,"vote_average":7.284,"vote_count":4323},"modified":"2023-07-18T10:28:38.000Z","cast":["Melissa Benoist","Chyler Leigh","David Harewood","Katie McGrath","Jesse Rath","Nicole Maines","Azie Tesfai","Julie Gonzalo","Staz Nair","Peta Sergeant"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Melissa Benoist","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Melissa Benoist","tmdb_id":129104,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fUPIkDDVmyZPejPu67HyfdDar9W.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/129104"},{"name":"Chyler Leigh","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chyler Leigh","tmdb_id":69210,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yoL8HbWhnoTVugTV5qLJP8gVpIq.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/69210"},{"name":"David Harewood","name_vi":null,"name_original":"David Harewood","tmdb_id":16752,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kjWRYwRGQco0C4p2iIh2RV86fi7.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/16752"},{"name":"Katie McGrath","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Katie McGrath","tmdb_id":150587,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cq9pc7qFRUKCrkXgsi5mJkb64U5.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/150587"},{"name":"Jesse Rath","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jesse Rath","tmdb_id":96593,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9t9BCb3LrV1hrIw0PJoBZOGUHVL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/96593"},{"name":"Nicole Maines","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Nicole Maines","tmdb_id":1718957,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g0Wv8JJBsHrGbF0ZlDBVIGUifwT.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1718957"},{"name":"Azie Tesfai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Azie Tes